data.description: Tucked away in a tranquil neighborhood lined with majestic oak trees, your new dream home waits for you! Lucie Lakes Estates is a charming neighborhood where residents are able to enjoy peace and serenity away from the buzz of the city, but still take advantage of the conveniences the city has to offer. This lovely home features an open living area with plenty of natural light, and front and back screened porches so you can enjoy Florida's natural beauty and delightful weather whether you're indoors or outdoors. For only $25 monthly in HOA dues, you'll have access to a spectacular heated pool, a cabana, and more within this well-maintained and welcoming community.
